            <div type="letter">
                  <pb facs="1038529" n="167r"/>
                  <p><lb/>Exanimatus pene sum <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> tristi nuntio, quem attulerunt <rs type="letter" key="B_1718-12-10_991170517039605501">litter<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> heri <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>
                        <lb/>me accept<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>. Ita ne ergo <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-120379260">Scheuchzero</rs> nostr<subst><del>a</del><add>o</add></subst> tanta injuria fiet, ut nequidem 
                        <lb/>nominatio ab <abbr>Exc.</abbr> et <abbr>Ill.mis</abbr> <abbr>Dnis</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089922930 pers_DE-588-1089586140 pers_DE-588-1111043582" type="persons"><abbr>Reff.</abbr></rs> facta et <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Collegio Sapientum
                        <lb/>confirmata <rs type="organisation">Senatui</rs> proponenda sit? Sed unde tanta rerum catastrophe?
                        <lb/>Metuo valde ab <abbr>Exc.<hi rend="sup">mo</hi></abbr> novo <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1111043582">Reformatore</rs>, quem nec Tibi favere, ali<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>quando mihi dictum fuit ab <rs type="person">y</rs>. Cum tanta sit inimicorum nostrorum
                        <lb/>potentia, ego fere in id adducor, ut constituam<del>,</del> nihil unquam, quamdiu
                        <lb/>in his oris degam, in lucem publicam emitt<subst><del>am</del><add>ere</add></subst>;<del>meque</del> ira enim et in<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dignatione co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>otus<del>,</del> indignos censeo hos homines, qui aliqua <subst><del>meis</del><add>mea</add></subst>
                        <lb/><del>oris </del>Venetiis aut <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3171728">Patavii</rs> impressa videant. Spero autem fore ali<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>quando occasionem, calumnias inimicorum meliore modo retunden<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>di. Dubito an proximis Bacchanalibus <rs type="place" key="place_VER-repven">Venetias</rs> iturus sim, rogo
                        <lb/>itaque, ut mihi brevibus causam tant<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> mutationis indices, et quid sibi
                        <lb/>velint ista verba Tua, <hi rend="u">coactus ab officio recedere debeo</hi>, patefacias.
                        <lb/>Si vereris talia scriptur<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>ittere, poteris uti secreto scribendi genere,
                        <lb/>substituendo pro singulis alphabeti litteris certum aliquem characterem,
                        <lb/>ego enim rem etiam sine clave intelligam.</p> <closer><salute>Vale et me ut hactenus ita
                              <lb/>porro ama. </salute><dateline><rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3171728">Patavii</rs> <date when="1718-12-12"><abbr>d.</abbr> 12. <abbr>Xbris.</abbr> 1718</date>.</dateline></closer>
                  <postscript><p><abbr>P. S.</abbr> Gratias ago pro transmissa
                        <pb facs="1038530" n="167v"/>
                        <lb/><rs type="letter">epistola</rs> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1156417392">Friderici Gutt</rs>, ante hos sex dies <rs type="letter">aliam</rs> accepi, quam <rs type="person">ami<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cus</rs> aliquis in <rs type="place" key="place_VER-polenk">Poloniam</rs> proficiscens afferre debebat, sed 12<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> <rs type="keyword">solidos</rs>
                        <lb/>pro portorio solvi, unde hoc eo magis miror, si Tu eandem <rs type="letter">episto<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lam</rs> ab <rs type="person">amico</rs> illo acceptam <rs type="place" key="place_VER-repven">Venetiis</rs> mihi transmisisti. Rogo ut 
                        <lb/>comburas hanc <rs type="letter" key="brieftag">epistolam</rs>.</p></postscript>
            </div>
